    public abstract class JonixExtractor
extends Object
    An abstract base-class for an extractor - a listener for JonixStreamer processing the events it fires as it parses an ONIX source. Subclasses are required to implement onHeaderElement(Element, JonixStreamer) and onProductElement(Element, JonixStreamer), but may also override the other protected methods.

    Users of an extractor can specify where to send the log messages using setLogger(PrintStream).

    NOTE: extractors may be reused over different streamers, if needed
